{#

    Address
    -------

    A component used to display a researcher's address or location inside an attribute block.
    Falls back to a default message when no value is provided.

    `value`: the address or location to display. Defaults to "Não fornecida." if empty.

    Content
    -------
    Not used. The display is handled via the `value` parameter.

    Usage
    -----

    To show a researcher's location:

        <researcher.Address value="São Paulo, SP" />

    If `value` is not provided or is empty, it will display:

        Não fornecida.

#}



{% set value = value or "Não fornecida." %}

<researcher.Attribute name="Localização">
    {{value}}
</researcher.Attribute>